// const routes = require('next-routes')
const routes = (module.exports = require('next-routes')());

routes                   // about  about     /about
    .add('home', '/home', 'index')
    .add('contact', '/about')
    .add('about', '/over-ons', 'over-ons')
    .add('references.index', '/referenties', '/referenties/')
    .add('references.show', '/referenties/:id', '/referenties/')
    .add('services.index', '/diensten/', '/diensten/') // in footer
    .add('services.show', '/diensten/:id', '/diensten/')
    .add('services.show', '/diensten/:id', '/diensten/')
